sources.description:
Daniel, an ex-soldier, gave up a violent life to live peacefully with his new wife. But when he steps in during a terrible incident at the local pub he sparks a gang war that can only end in an explosive battle in the Australian outback.
2014.  Stars: Rod Manikam, Simon Arblaster, Maggie Meyer
